'''Klickibunti''' is a [[German language|German]] term which translates roughly as "Clicky-shiny".  It is a derisive term for overblown [[Graphical User Interface|Graphical User Interfaces]], with the implicit assertion being that a simpler scheme or a nice [[Command line interface]] would be superior.

